Description: 31 & Company focuses on helping applicants through the college admissions process, college internships, and fellowship searches.
Headquarters Regions: Dallas/Fort Worth Metroplex, Southern US
Full Description: 31 & Company was founded in June 2021 with the intention of navigating low-income and other disadvantaged applicants through the college admissions process and continuing college internship and fellowship search. Graduating college seniors and recent college graduates can also expect academic and career counseling, along with subsidized test and interview preparation. As further service to low-income and disadvantaged members of society, 31 & Company is interested in assisting corporations and other large organizations cater to minority applicants and workers in order to best attract and retain diverse talent. Alongside various academic and career mentors, specialists, and counselors, low-income and disadvantaged youth can learn how experienced and proven minority applicants managed to turn supposed weaknesses (i.e lack of resources and intensive career planning) into diverse strengths that helped them stand out in the talent pool. Low-income and disadvantaged applicants are constantly overlooked in favor of wealthier applicants with higher test scores and expensive private counseling experience. 31 & Company aims to bridge that gap by accentuating personal strengths rather than focusing on material weaknesses. Although standardized testing and intensive interview preparation are key components of the college admissions process and college internship and fellowship search, 31 & Company focuses just as intimately on personal strengths that will supplement an applicant’s background and interests.

Headquarters Regions: Midwestern US
Full Description: CapAssist is owned and operated by a group of individual business owners with a combined experience of nearly 50 years in business-to-business financing. Located in the heartland of America, they are not a massive Wall Street firm, and they are also not a traditional bank. Having built companies from one employee to 400, they know what it takes to build a successful independent business. Because of this, everything they do comes from a small business owner mentality. They know that times may come when the difference between a good month and a bad month is the additional inventory to make just one more sale, or being able to hire just one more employee. Having a partner who can provide working capital can be a key factor in your business' success. They don't want a lack of capital funding to be an obstacle for your business growth. That is why they are here. They understand the world of business financing and business credit. They know what is often required when you're looking for someone to help you with your capital funding needs. They know you are busy, and often have little to no free time any given day of the week. That is why they try to make it fast and easy to get the capital funding you need. And, their merchant cash advance offers you more flexibility and freedom than standard business loans. They know what it takes to get your business from point A to point B. If a little extra working capital is the missing element, they want to partner with you. Their goal is to help you succeed. As your business grows, they want to grow with you as your capital funding source. Let's build your dream together.

Description: New Home Search
Headquarters Regions: Greater Houston Area, Southern US
Full Description: Houston's New Homes provide a variety of real estate services for home buyers and home builders. Our buyer's agents help you find new homes and home builders. We make the new home buying process in Houston easier. Our #1 goal is to provide you with an unparalleled home buying experience. First we conduct a thorough interview and consultation in person, by phone or email. During this interview we'll discover everything you may want and need in purchasing your new home. Then we conduct a thorough home and community search based on the information we've gathered from you. During this process, we'll get you qualified for a home loan, negotiate the best price on your behalf and ensure a seamless closing process. Soon you'll be moving into your new house. Many ask: Who pays for our services? The seller or new home builder. See Buyer's Agent below for more on your Texas rights to have buyer representation. Our buyer's agents are real estate agents who work exclusively with the home buyer and never represent sellers. Working with a buyer's agent will not cost you anything; the seller/home builder, has already agreed to pay the buyer's agent once everything is final on your new home. The job of the buyer's agent is to help you find the right home, select the right builder and negotiate the best price and incentives for you. They provide the true facts involving the value of your new home, the market and neighborhood conditions and any physical defects on the property. In Houston, and other areas of Texas, buyers have certain rights; when you sign an agreement with a real estate agent, that agent then works for you and have your best interest in mind. In Texas, you are not considered represented until you've entered an agreement with a real estate agent. Using a buyer's agent is like using an attorney, except you don't pay for the buyers agents' representation. We are here to help you through the entire home buying process without you having to do much searching and hassling through the entire buying process. After many years visiting with home buyers We've found a lot of their experiences have been very similar; They've told us they were exhausted in their home search, aggravated at the home buying process, and frustrated by previous Realtor and builder experiences. While in their pursuit in purchasing their new home they felt like they were still at the beginning of the home buying process. Some have even given up on purchasing a home entirely. Even if you've bought a home before, you probably wouldn't want to experience what you've gone through before. Houston's New Homes is here to help find your dream home without the hassle.
